Package: sirad
Type: Package
Title: Functions for calculating daily solar radiation
Version: 1.0-7
Date: 2011-10-20
Author: Jedrzej Bojanowski
Maintainer: Jedrzej Bojanowski <jedrzej.bojanowski@gmail.com>
Description: Package provides functions to calculate daily solar radiation at horizontal surface using several well-known models. It also includes functions for model calibration based on groud-truth data as well as a function for auto-calibration.
Depends: zoo, ncdf, RNetCDF
License: GPL-2
LazyLoad: yes
